Nollywood actress, Nkechi Blessing Sunday, has announced that she has found a new lover. Her announcement came a few hours after confirming that her marriage to Opeyemi Falegan had crashed. Nkechi Blessing in a new Instagram live with James Brown and some other participants, revealed that she’s currently dating a 60-year-old man. The actress said: “I’m dating a 60-year-old man now and he gives me so much peace. “He does not have time for Instagram. I’m the one sharing all these scandals to him.” When asked if he’s not too old for her, Nkechi Blessing said, “do you know the 60-year-old man I’m talking about? He lives in America and is younger than all of you on this live video.” This is coming after the actress’s husband, Opeyemi Falegan confirmed that he is no longer married to Nkechi Blessing whom he described as a lesbian. Responding, Nkechi also revealed that her ex-husband does not perform well in bed.